Package commodities.tests

Class Summary
Recommendation Recommendation contains a test's recommendation on what action to take with a commodity (buy/sell).
RecommendationAnalyzer RecommendationAnalyzer is a threaded check of recommendations for contracts.
TestIdentifier The TestIdentifier class contains the Test Id and the class used for the test so that the TestManager can track which tests are best for a given commodity.
TestManager The TestManager class controls what tests are available to the system and how they are accessed.
TestOptimizer TestOptimizer controls the optimization of the technical tests.
